{"tid":1397062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"臨時立法會對奪權之重要性","createTime":"2019-08-02T10:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T15:57:00.000Z","uid":133519,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dfb460106a63e920e848ab757aa803cf6617673d","tid":1397062,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:02:00.000Z","msg":"史例：<br />\n愛爾蘭共和國（英語：Irish Republic，愛爾蘭語：Saorst&aacute;t &Eacute;ireann），字面意思為「愛爾蘭的共和國」，是由1916年復活節起義中宣告，<span style=\"color: red;\">1919年由第一屆愛爾蘭國會成立的單方獨立宣言的愛爾蘭國家</span>。<br />\n<br />\n第一屆愛爾蘭國會(英語：The First D&aacute;il，愛爾蘭語：An Ch&eacute;ad D&aacute;il)是於1919至1921年召集的愛爾蘭國會。 1919年在英國議會選舉中獲勝的候選人拒絕承認英國國會，<span style=\"color: red;\">自行成立一院制的革命議會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當然立法會要成功亦要勇武派</span><br />\n<br />\n愛爾蘭獨立戰爭：<br />\n愛爾蘭共和軍在愛爾蘭發動的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">游擊戰</span></span>，以反對大不列顛及愛爾蘭聯合王國對愛爾蘭的統治。"},{"pid":"a7bf7a9ca22ca28216c41fb36cff43f374c6f300","tid":1397062,"uid":133519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:04:12.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},{"pid":"26eeea4b91dca0186bcd598384c82cc1fff136db","tid":1397062,"uid":133519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:05:32.000Z","msg":"1919年在英國議會選舉中獲勝的候選人拒絕承認英國國會，自行成立一院制的革命議會。<br />\n<br />\n要成功，就要令泛民有獨立革命，推到重來嘅心，不過而家未有，泛民仲未豁出去"},{"pid":"b24fd92c0e6922e9c6ecd7e3d5150418cd38d3ce","tid":1397062,"uid":288924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effaad3e918ede472a8b834ec18f69278ba90c17","tid":1397062,"uid":14830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:09:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cb1e6e0064d43e76cbf7644089f9ab652e557d4","tid":1397062,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:09:12.000Z","msg":"大約想幾時宣佈先"},{"pid":"22815687ea6ed3fb7c208ef272309fa74f126923","tid":1397062,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cb1e6e0064d43e76cbf7644089f9ab652e557d4","tid":1397062,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:09:12.000Z","msg":"大約想幾時宣佈先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:11:58.000Z","msg":"真係要靠一個組織，議會宣布先有説服力同有效運動，唔係就好似9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb135a151cd494637f4f9c6da5e60a50da7e440b","tid":1397062,"uid":33473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n成立呢個立法會<br />\n大機會要出樣<br />\n因為唔出樣認受性幾乎係無<br />\n但一出樣，失敗之後義士會面臨比暴動罪更嚴重的後果<br />\n所以行之前一定要小心"},{"pid":"f2ec9839cdde5701ffe7cfcd04586c66ed317afd","tid":1397062,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:37:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7512ec813e8c74fa0e80702651c24aee181cbfad","tid":1397062,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb135a151cd494637f4f9c6da5e60a50da7e440b","tid":1397062,"uid":33473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n成立呢個立法會<br />\n大機會要出樣<br />\n因為唔出樣認受性幾乎係無<br />\n但一出樣，失敗之後義士會面臨比暴動罪更嚴重的後果<br />\n所以行之前一定要小心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:39:34.000Z","msg":"泛民一定唔敢做，佢哋仲想喺框架入面爭扎。要有個人，我希望陳浩天可以做，不過要多啲人支持返佢。"},{"pid":"58b550bac2d0546e811376ee5ab66677326ceb3d","tid":1397062,"uid":246118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:42:39.000Z","msg":"【7.21之後】無大台無領袖的議會是這樣煉成的（附臨時議會功能＆目標）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1365105\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1365105</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c8fbb45b28a9d8608a6186efb4e85e7c70a4c0b1","tid":1397062,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02